\c 13
\s IN\nd kosi\nd* ilaya uJoshuwa ukuthi abele izizwe zakoIsrayeli ilizwe elinqotshiweyo
\p
\v 1 UJoshuwa wayesemdala eleminyaka eminengi. IN\nd kosi\nd* yasisithi kuye: Usumdala, uleminyaka eminengi, kusasele ilizwe elikhulu kakhulu ukudla ilifa lalo\x + 23.1; 14.10.\x*.
\v 2 Yileli ilizwe eliseleyo\x + Hlu. 3.1-4.\x*: Yonke imingcele yamaFilisti\x + Jow. 3.4; Josh. 22.10,11.\x*, leGeshuri yonke\x + 1 Sam. 27.8; 12.5; 11,13.\x*,
\v 3 kusukela eShihori eliphambi kweGibhithe, kusiya emngceleni weEkhironi enyakatho, elibalelwa kumaKhanani\x + 1 Lan. 13.5. Jer. 2.18.\x*; ababusi abahlanu bamaFilisti\x + Hlu. 3.3. 16.30. 1 Sam. 5.8,11. 6.4,12,16,18. 7.7; 29.6,7.\x*, abeGaza, labeAshidodi, abeAshikeloni, abeGathi, labeEkhironi\x + 15.11.\x*, labeAvi\x + Dute. 2.23.\x*,
\v 4 kusukela eningizimu, ilizwe lonke lamaKhanani, leMeyara elingelamaSidoni, kuze kufike eAfeki\x + 12.18.\x*, kuze kube semngceleni wamaAmori\x + Hlu. 1.34,36.\x*,
\v 5 lelizwe lamaGebali, leLebhanoni lonke, kusiya empumalanga\x + 1 Kho. 5.18. Hlab. 83.7. Hez. 27.9.\x*, kusukela eBhali-Gadi ngaphansi kwentaba yeHermoni\x + 11.17. 12.7.\x*, kusiya ekungeneni kweHamathi\x + Nani 34.8.\x*.
\v 6 Bonke abakhileyo ezintabeni, kusukela eLebhanoni kusiya eMisirefothi-Mayimi, wonke amaSidoni\x + 11.8.\x*, mina ngizabaxotsha elifeni phambi kwabantwana bakoIsrayeli\x + 23.13. Hlu. 2.21,23.\x*. Kuphela ulabele uIsrayeli ngenkatho libe yilifa, njengoba ngikulayile\x + 23.4. Nani 34.2. Hlu. 18.1. Hlab. 16.6.\x*.
\v 7 Ngakho-ke yehlukanisa ilizwe leli libe yilifa ezizweni eziyisificamunwemunye lengxenye yesizwe sakoManase.
\s Ilizwe elanikwa isizwe sakoRubeni lesakoGadi lengxenye yesizwe sakoManase
\p
\v 8 Kanye labo abakoRubeni labakoGadi bemukela ilifa labo, uMozisi owabanika lona, ngaphetsheya kweJordani ngempumalanga, njengalokho uMozisi inceku yeN\nd kosi\nd* wabanika\x + Nani 32.33. Dute. 3.12,13. 29.8. 12.6. 22.4.\x*:
\v 9 Kusukela eAroweri esekhunjini lwesifula seArinoni, lomuzi ophakathi kwesifula\x + Dute. 2.36.\x*, lamagceke wonke\x + Dute. 3.10.\x* eMedeba\x + 13.16,17; Nani 21.30.\x* kuze kube seDiboni\x + 13.16,17; Nani 21.30.\x*,
\v 10 lemizi yonke kaSihoni inkosi yamaAmori owabusa eHeshiboni\x + Nani 21.24,25.\x*, kuze kube semngceleni wabantwana bakoAmoni,
\v 11 leGileyadi\x + 12.5.\x* lomngcele wamaGeshuri lamaMahakathi\x + 13.13. Dute. 3.14.\x* lentaba yonke yeHermoni\x + Dute. 3.9.\x* leBashani lonke kuze kube seSaleka\x + 12.5.\x*,
\v 12 umbuso wonke kaOgi eBashani owabusa eAshitarothi leEdreyi\x + 12.4.\x*. Nguye owasala kunsali yeziqhwaga\x + 12.4.\x*. UMozisi wayebatshaye-ke wabaxotsha elifeni labo.
\v 13 Kodwa abantwana bakoIsrayeli kabawaxotshanga elifeni amaGeshuri lamaMahakathi; kodwa amaGeshuri lamaMahakathi ahlala phakathi kukaIsrayeli kuze kube lamuhla\x + 13.11.\x*.
\v 14 Kuphela esizweni sakoLevi kanikanga ilifa; iminikelo yeN\nd kosi\nd* uNkulunkulu kaIsrayeli eyenziwe ngomlilo iyilifa laso\x + Nani 18.20.\x*, njengokutsho kwayo kuso\x + 13.33.\x*.
\p
\v 15 UMozisi wasenika isizwe sabantwana bakoRubeni ngokwensendo zabo.
\v 16 Lomngcele waso wasukela eAroweri\x + 13.9.\x* esekhunjini lwesifula seArinoni, lomuzi ophakathi kwesifula, lamagceke\x + 13.9.\x* wonke eMedeba\x + 13.9.\x*,
\v 17 iHeshiboni, lemizi yayo yonke esemagcekeni\x + 13.9.\x*, iDiboni\x + 13.9.\x* leBamothi-Bhali leBeti-Bhali-Meyoni,
\v 18 leJahaza\x + 21.36. 1 Lan. 6.78. Nani 21.23.\x* leKedemothi\x + 21.37. 1 Lan. 6.79.\x* leMefahathi\x + 21.37. 1 Lan. 6.79.\x*,
\v 19 leKiriyathayimi\x + Nani 32.37. Hez. 25. 9.\x* leSibima leZerethi-Shahari entabeni yesigodi\x + Nani 32.38. Isa. 16.8,9. Jer. 48.32.\x*,
\v 20 leBeti-Peyori\x + Dute.4.46; Nani 23.28.\x* leAshidodi-Pisiga leBeti-Jeshimothi\x + 12.3.\x*,
\v 21 lemizi yonke yamagceke, lombuso wonke kaSihoni inkosi yamaAmori, owayebusa eHeshiboni\x + Dute. 3.10.\x*, uMozisi amtshaya\x + Nani 21.24.\x* leziphathamandla zeMidiyani\x + Nani 31.8.\x*, oEvi loRekemi loZuri loHuri loReba, amakhosana kaSihoni, abakhileyo belizwe\x + Hlab. 83.11. Hez. 32.30. Dan. 11.8. Mika 5.5.\x*.
\p
\v 22 LoBalami indodana kaPeyori\x + Nani 31.8.\x*, ovumisayo, abantwana bakoIsrayeli bambulala ngenkemba phakathi kwababuleweyo babo.
\v 23 Lomngcele wabantwana bakoRubeni wawuyiJordani lomngcele \add wayo\add*. Lokhu kwakuyilifa labantwana bakoRubeni ngokwensendo zabo, imizi lemizana yayo.
\p
\v 24 UMozisi wasenika isizwe sakoGadi, kubantwana bakoGadi ngokwensendo zabo.
\v 25 Lomngcele wabo wawuyiJazeri\x + Nani 21.32; 32.35.\x* layo yonke imizi yeGileyadi lengxenye yelizwe labantwana bakoAmoni\x + Nani 21.26,28,29; Dute. 2.19. Hlu. 11.13-27.\x*, kusiya eAroweri, ephambi kweRaba\x + Dute. 3.11.\x*,
\v 26 njalo kusukela eHeshiboni kusiya eRamathi-Mizipa leBetonimi\x + 11.3.\x*, njalo kusukela eMahanayimi\x + 2 Sam. 17.24.\x* kuze kube semngceleni weDebhiri\x + 2 Sam. 9.4,5; 17.27.\x*;
\v 27 lesigodini, iBeti-Harama\x + Nani 32.36.\x* leBeti-Nimira\x + Nani 32.3,36.\x* leSukothi leZafoni, insali yombuso kaSihoni inkosi yeHeshiboni, iJordani lomngcele\x + Gen. 33.17. 1 Kho. 7.46. 2 Lan. 4.17.\x*, kuze kube sekupheleni kolwandle lweKinerethi ngaphetsheya kweJordani empumalanga\x + Nani 34.11; 11.2; 12.3.\x*.
\v 28 Leli yilifa labantwana bakoGadi ngokwensendo zabo, imizi lemizana yabo.
\p
\v 29 UMozisi wasenika ingxenye yesizwe sakoManase \add ilifa\add*; njalo yayingeyengxenye yesizwe sabantwana bakoManase ngokwensendo zabo.
\v 30 Lomngcele wabo wasukela eMahanayimi, iBashani lonke, umbuso wonke kaOgi inkosi yeBashani, layo yonke imizana yeJayiri eseBashani, imizi engamatshumi ayisithupha\x + Dute. 3.14. 1 Lan. 2.23. Nani 32.41.\x*.
\v 31 Lengxenye yeGileyadi, leAshitarothi, leEdreyi, imizi yombuso kaOgi eBashani, yayingeyabantwana bakoMakiri indodana kaManase\x + 12.4.\x*, \add ngitsho\add* eyengxenye yabantwana bakoMakiri ngokwensendo zabo\x + 17.1.\x*.
\v 32 La yiwo uMozisi awanika aba yilifa emagcekeni akoMowabi ngaphetsheya kweJordani eJeriko empumalanga\x + Nani 22.1.\x*.
\p
\v 33 Kodwa esizweni sakoLevi uMozisi kanikanga ilifa\x + 13.14; 18.7.\x*; iN\nd kosi\nd*, uNkulunkulu kaIsrayeli, iyilifa labo, njengokutsho kwayo kubo\x + Nani 18.20.\x*.